cast.name: 奥利维亚·罗德里戈 Olivia Rodrigo

director.name: 克里·阿斯姆森 Kerry Asmussen

this_title: Olivia Rodrigo：Live from the Ace Theatre (Amex Member Week Performance)
trans_title: 奥利维亚罗德里戈：AMEX特别演出
introduction: Olivia Rodrigo will stop by the Theatre at Ace Hotel on Monday, Oct. 9 for an intimate evening performance before embarking on her highly-anticipated GUTS World Tour in 2024.The event is in celebration of the third annual Amex Member Week, providing an experience exclusively for American Express Card Members. Attendees can look forward to seeing GUTS live: Rodrigo’s recent, widely celebrated, sophomore album.“I’ve been excited by the response to GUTS and I can’t wait to perform live for my fans,” Rodrigo said. “Partnering with American Express for my GUTS world tour, the GUTS Gallery pop-up experiences, and now this intimate performance for my fans means so much.”
